text: Pervushino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starokamyshlinsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 440 as of 2010. There are 17 streets. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Kushnarenkovo, 10 km from Starye Kamyshly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Pervushino
